 abundance\nuncertainties. This is the first science demonstration of multi-object adaptive\noptics with high resolution infrared spectroscopy, and we also discuss the\nfeasibility of this technique for use in the upcoming era of 30-m class\ntelescope facilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2016 21:00:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-28"}
