tions to affect the\nresiliency of a conjugate gradient solver application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2016 05:49:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 05:49:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
