ht\ncurves and spectra. It can also potentially explain the frequency-dependent\ntime delay seen in radio flare light curves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2016 12:48:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2017 00:57:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-19"}
